data.description: This one level home and horse property needs a bit of TLC and is perfect for the buyer who wants to build some equity through repairs and updates. Ask your lender if a rehab loan is right for you. Seller is replacing master bath flooring and removing wallpaper & painting the wall in the kitchen. There is a temporary wall for a 4th bedroom space just past the big pantry area, that can be removed/restored to the prior sitting area. Huge mud room and entry just off the kitchen.  Enjoy the 40x40 shop/barn, loafing shed, chicken coop, tac shed w/ power, and small greenhouse. Seller leaving 3 out of the 4 square pens, but taking the round pen and round metal hay feeder.  Hot tub and Gazebo do not convey. Shares of BBWA ditch water w/ control of your own head gate offers irrigation/animal watering from April-Oct. RV parking/hookups w/ septic dump available. Well, not usable, cistern only.
